trans-unit.source: Specifies the visual state of a group box that is drawn with visual styles.
trans-unit.target: 비주얼 스타일으로 그려진 그룹 상자의 시각적 상태를 지정 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The GroupBoxState values correspond to the states of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement> objects exposed by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement.Button.GroupBox> class.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement>개체 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement.Button.GroupBox>클래스</xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement.Button.GroupBox> 에 의해 노출</xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleElement> 된 상태에 해당 하는 GroupBoxState 값

trans-unit.source: The GroupBoxState values are also used as an argument in the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.GroupBoxRenderer.DrawGroupBox%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method.
trans-unit.target: GroupBoxState 값 중 하나에으로 사용 되는 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.GroupBoxRenderer.DrawGroupBox%2A?displayProperty=fullName>메서드.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.GroupBoxRenderer.DrawGroupBox%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The group box has the default appearance.
